			<div class="content" id="post-content-2801668">
									

<p>This is a proof-of-concept and template for a GOI-format that hopefully you'll be seeing more of soon.</p>
<p>The IJAMEA has become something of a passion project of mine recently, and we're working on a hub, which will be out soonish.</p>
<p>Everyone is free to use the CSS module for their own IJAMEA work (and encouraged to do so).</p>
<p>Thanks to MrWrong, Roget, and everyone else who peaked at this in chat.</p>
<p>EDIT: w/r/t yokai vs youkai: &quot;youkai&quot; is our settled upon spelling for use in the battalion, &quot;yokai&quot; is my preferred romanization. If this really bothers people, I will change it.</p>
<p>EDIT2: in case you didnt get it, this references MrWrong's <a href="/scp-2511">SCP-2511</a> and my own <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">SCP-2235</span></p>

